	<td bgcolor="#000000" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" > <b></b></font>
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >interesting that in high aggro situations 4 keeps appearing -maybe a set formula rather than just fixed hate values to regain aggro if the aggro is too high to regain normally?</font></p>
	
